snippet.title: CyberSphere Online - Gameplay Trailer 1.2
snippet.description:
Google Play: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.lb4business.cybersphereonline
App Store: https://itunes.apple.com/app/cybersphere-online/id1288087518

3d shooter in sci-fi setting with online multiplayer (Deathmatch and Coop). Join forces with players from all over the world to stop alien robot invasion!

Music by Wav maniacs https://www.facebook.com/wavmaniacs
